The '''100th [[Pennsylvania House of Representatives]] District''' is located in [[Lancaster County, Pennsylvania|Lancaster County]] and includes the following areas:<ref>{{cite web |title=Composite Listing of House of Representatives Districts |publisher=[[Pennsylvania Department of State]] |url=http://www.dos.state.pa.us/bcel/cwp/view.asp?a=1099&q=431805 |accessdate=2008-11-01}}</ref>
{{col-begin}}
{{col-2}}
* [[Bart Township, Pennsylvania|Bart Township]]
* [[Christiana, Pennsylvania|Christiana]]
* [[Colerain Township, Lancaster County, Pennsylvania|Colerain Township]]
* [[Conestoga Township, Pennsylvania|Conestoga Township]]
* [[Drumore Township, Pennsylvania|Drumore Township]]
* [[East Drumore Township, Pennsylvania|East Drumore Township]]
* [[Eden Township, Pennsylvania|Eden Township]]
* [[Fulton Township, Pennsylvania|Fulton Township]]
* [[Leacock Township, Pennsylvania|Leacock Township]]
* [[Little Britain Township, Pennsylvania|Little Britain Township]]
{{col-2}}
* [[Manor Township, Lancaster County, Pennsylvania|Manor Township]] (PART)
** District Indiantown
* [[Martic Township, Pennsylvania|Martic Township]]
* [[Paradise Township, Lancaster County, Pennsylvania|Paradise Township]]
* [[Providence Township, Pennsylvania|Providence Township]]
* [[Quarryville, Pennsylvania|Quarryville]]
* [[Sadsbury Township, Lancaster County, Pennsylvania|Sadsbury Township]]
* [[Strasburg, Pennsylvania|Strasburg]]
* [[Strasburg Township, Pennsylvania|Strasburg Township]]
{{col-end}}

